<HEAD>Iran Executes 10</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NICOSIA, Cyprus (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Iran executed 10 ``counterrevolutionaries
and Iraqi spies'' on Sunday, Iranian television reported.
   The state-run television said the executions were carried out
after the sentences were reviewed and approved by the Supreme
